{"id":1008,"date":"2014-03-12T22:53:53","date_gmt":"2014-03-12T22:53:53","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/twelvershia.net\/?p=1008"},"modified":"2014-03-12T22:53:53","modified_gmt":"2014-03-12T22:53:53","slug":"response-to-biased-bukhari-2","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/2014\/03\/12\/response-to-biased-bukhari-2\/","title":{"rendered":"Response to: Biased Bukhari \u2013 2"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/imgstore.org\/a\/67hxw0egsgub?i=1008\" alt=\"\" \/><strong>The following is a response to SlaveOfAhlubait\u2019s article entitled: Biased Bukhari \u2013 2, which can be found <a href=\"http:\/\/ahlubait.wordpress.com\/2010\/04\/20\/biased-bukhari-2\/\" rel=\"external nofollow\">here<\/a>.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">SoA, in this article, quotes a couple of narrations in an attempt to show that Al-Bukhari used to hide the names of a Sahabi that is accused of a sin.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nThis accusation against Al-Bukhari has been raised by ShiaPen previously and we have responded to this accusation in another refutation, which can be found <a href=\"http:\/\/twelvershia.net\/2014\/03\/03\/response-to-efforts-of-bukhari-to-hide-identity-of-alcohol-seller-sahabi\/\" rel=\"external nofollow\">here<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nIn short, Al-Bukhari has narrated this tradition along with another scholar of his time, Abu Bakr Mohammad bin Abi Khalid Al-Sawma\u2019ee Al-Tabari, which therefore means that Al-Bukhari did not err in this narration, nor did he tamper with it. Al-Thahabi has a biography in Tareekh Al-Islam of the latter. However, he has named him Abu Bakr Mohammad bin Khalid Al-Sawma\u2019ee Al-Tabari accidentally.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<div class=\"mh-excerpt\"><p>The following is a response to SlaveOfAhlubait\u2019s article entitled: Biased Bukhari \u2013 2, which can be found here. SoA, in this article, quotes a couple of narrations in an attempt to show that Al-Bukhari used to hide the names of <a class=\"mh-excerpt-more\" href=\"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/2014\/03\/12\/response-to-biased-bukhari-2\/\" title=\"Response to: Biased Bukhari \u2013 2\">[read more]<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":3894,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-1008","1":"post","2":"type-post","3":"status-publish","4":"format-standard","5":"has-post-thumbnail","7":"category-hadith"},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1008","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1008"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1008\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1011,"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1008\/revisions\/1011"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3894"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1008"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1008"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1008"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}